    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国更倾向于与印度合作建设耗资 10 亿美元的河流项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/bangldesh-prefers-india-over-china-in-1-billion-river-project</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国总理谢赫·哈西娜表示，孟加拉国政府希望邻国印度实施一项耗资 10 亿美元的河流开发项目，此举将缓解新德里的安全担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/bangldesh-prefers-india-over-china-in-1-billion-river-project</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 07:58:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国将于下月招募 140 亿美元刺激计划的受助者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/thailand-to-enrol-recipients-of-14-billion-stimulus-next-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国将于下个月开始登记有资格获得政府现金援助的公民，这是刺激东南亚第二大经济体约 140 亿美元计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/thailand-to-enrol-recipients-of-14-billion-stimulus-next-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 06:56:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>审计人员称法国解决“令人担忧”财政问题的计划缺乏可信度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/french-audit-court-says-deficit-gap-versus-eu-is-unacceptable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国国家审计长警告称，当前修复“令人担忧”的公共财政的计划已经缺乏可信度，就像那些推行扩张性税收和支出政策的政治团体在提前选举后争相组建新政府一样。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/french-audit-court-says-deficit-gap-versus-eu-is-unacceptable</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 06:15:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球变暖导致世界电网瘫痪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/climate-change-leaves-world-s-electricity-networks-unable-to-cope</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从阿尔巴尼亚到德克萨斯州的停电事件表明电网尚未做好应对气候变化的准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/climate-change-leaves-world-s-electricity-networks-unable-to-cope</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 04:00:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>唐纳德·特朗普邀请曾经的竞争对手妮基·黑利参加共和党大会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/donald-trump-after-shooting-asked-nikki-haley-to-attend-rnc-convention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，前总统唐纳德·特朗普致电前联合国大使、他 2024 年竞选中的曾经的竞争对手妮基·黑利，并邀请她参加本周在威斯康星州密尔沃基举行的共和党全国代表大会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/donald-trump-after-shooting-asked-nikki-haley-to-attend-rnc-convention</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 02:12:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登罕见在椭圆形办公室发表讲话 呼吁民众在特朗普枪击事件后团结起来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/biden-speech-biden-calls-for-unity-after-trump-s-shooting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普遭遇暗杀后，总统乔·拜登恳请候选人冷静言论，并警告说国家正走向一条危险的道路，暴力将颠覆美国人的意愿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/biden-speech-biden-calls-for-unity-after-trump-s-shooting</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 00:37:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普枪击事件后，美国特勤局面临严格审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-secret-service-faces-intense-scrutiny-after-trump-shooting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普遭暗杀事件发生后，美国特勤局这个有着不光彩过去的机构被推到了政治风暴的中心，正面临公众的严厉审查和调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-secret-service-faces-intense-scrutiny-after-trump-shooting</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 21:53:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球市场在反弹后“特朗普交易”增多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/global-markets-ramp-up-the-trump-trade-after-rally-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普遇刺未遂之后，随着世界金融市场重新开放，有一件事似乎是可能的：特朗普的交易将获得更大的动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/global-markets-ramp-up-the-trump-trade-after-rally-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士信贷中期审查抨击瑞士金融市场监管局和瑞士央行，SZ 称</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/interim-credit-suisse-review-blasts-finma-and-snb-sz-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《周日报》报道，瑞士议会委员会对瑞信2023年破产案的审查得出的初步结论，严厉批评了金融监管机构Finma以及瑞士央行和政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/interim-credit-suisse-review-blasts-finma-and-snb-sz-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 13:36:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普枪击事件后乐观情绪推动加密货币价格上涨，比特币上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/bitcoin-btc-rises-as-trump-rally-shooting-seen-increasing-re-election-odds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普对暗杀企图作出坚决回应，引发人们猜测这位支持加密货币的前总统赢得连任的机会有所增加，随后比特币出现了近两个月来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/bitcoin-btc-rises-as-trump-rally-shooting-seen-increasing-re-election-odds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 02:44:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
